Date: 0/0/1925
Source: Soldier and Sailor Words
Author: FRASER & GIBBONS
Vol / Page: 310
Edition:
Quote: <i>WOZZER, THE: </i>The name among the Australians in Egypt for the street `Haret el Wazza' in Cairo, a low neighbourhood. Two encounters there in 1915 between police and native mobs were given the name of the `Battle of the Wozzer'.
Notes:

Date: 0/0/1936
